cast.overview: When Mahendra, the son of Bāhubali, learns about his heritage, he begins to look for answers. His story is juxtaposed with past events that unfolded in the Mahishmati Kingdom.
cast.title: Bāhubali 2: The Conclusion

details.biography: Ashrita Vemuganti, a Bharatanatyam and Kuchipudi dancer who was seen in SS Rajamouli’s magnum opus Baahuabli 2 : The Conclusion starring Prabhas,  Rana Daggubati, Tamannah Bhatia, Anushka Shetty and Ramya Krishna, has been roped in ‘Yatra’ in which  Malayalam superstar Mammootty is playing the role of late Chief Minister YS Rajasekhar Reddy. In Baahubali 2, Ashrita played the role of Anushka’s brother’s wife and she was also seen in Baahubali’s “Kanna Nidurinchara” song.
details.name: Ashrita Vemuganti
